Section 1. That section 2923.251 of the Revised Code be 4
enacted to read as follows: 5
Sec. 2923.251. (A) The department of children and youth, 6
in conjunction with the department of public safety, shall 7
develop and provide an informational notice in English, Spanish, 8
and Arabic that contains information and best practices 9
